                    <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                      <locus from="215r" facs="218">Fols 215r and following</locus>
                      Colophon, including note of ownership.:
                      <q>“This Psalter belongs to Wäldä Täklä Haymanot of Ğärr, son of Mark, the Evangelist, servant of Our Lord Jesus Christ.
                        It was finished on the month of Sane 17, 1918 (E.C.),EC), in the year of Mark, the Evangelist,
                        during the reign of our Empress Askalä Maryam [Zǝwditu, 1916–1930], daughter of King of Kings Mǝnilǝk of Ethiopia.
                        The one who steals or deletes is condemned.”</q>
                    </colophon>
                  </msItem>

